data.description: Wonderful new listing in Highlander Acres  subdivision! This 1 1/2 story home features 5 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bath, 2 car garage with fenced back yard. 30' round pool with deck and a nice outbuilding for storage. On the main level of the home you will find the owners suite, laundry room, 1/2 bathroom for guests and an open concept living room/kitchen/dining room. Kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, soft-close cabinetry, a wine fridge, and pantry. The living room has a vaulted ceiling with a stone covered gas fireplace. The owner's suite has a large walk in closet and full bathroom. Upstairs you will find another full bathroom and 4 nice size bedrooms with large closets. You will love that this home is on a cul-d-sac with low traffic. Vivent security. East Heights school district. Close to restaurants, shopping, and schools. Check it out!
